@21 = ~A Demonic Scroll

Sandrah has found another bit of information from our mysterious scroll. Someone named Alzaligundrel is the master of this scroll. He has an archenemy in some mountains in the south. The enemy's lair seems to be near falling water. So what? All of it is still too vague to divert us from our task. I am waiting for Sandra or her father to find out more.~
@22 = ~ The demonic scroll in you inventory seems to come alive. 
