@108 = ~The Failed Journey to Waterdeep

Sandrah had invited us to her father's house in Waterdeep. On the road we encountered a frightening bandit leader who had kidnappped a child. I refused to interfer myself and proposed to leave the case to the Waterdeep militia. Sandrah has left my group without a word and went to help the poor child's mother and to restore her reputation in her hometown. Without Sandrah and her map we could not travel on to Waterdeep. After a long odyssee in the wilderness we finally found our way back to the Friendly Arm. Will I ever see Sandrah again?~
