@167 = ~You cannot decipher the foreign writing ~
@168 = ~ ... today the Orloth has sent me to follow a group of travellers from Waterdeep. He thinks they are in possession of two of the creatures the master requires...
...
...during endless days persuing the small group. They carry two small ones indeed and are eagerly trying to hide their true destination by meandering across this damned land of the Sword Coast...
...
...the group was attacked by a band of bandits before I could get close to at least one of the childs. I was hiding in the brushes when I saw this DROW warrior priestess approaching...
