@213 = ~A Strange Piece of Cloth - Reconstructed

During your travels all over the Sword Coast, you and Sandrah have found three pieces of a strange cloth in various places. With the third piece in hand, you are finally able to reconstruct it. The reconstruction has given Sandrah the necessary clues. It is a bedcloth from Elminster's and Khalindra's household. 
Obviously it was used for Khalindra's second baby, the Bhaalspawn, during the time when it travelled from Waterdeep to an unknown destination in order to hide it from several groups of persuers. 
But why this was done? 
Who were the persuers?  
